description: HLA class I ligandome dataset obtained from hepatocellular carcinoma (HCC) as well as corresponding adjacent benign liver tissue (n=16) characterizing respective HLA immunoprecipitates. Additionally, from a subset of the mentioned HCC/ adjacent benign liver samples datasets gained from shotgun protein identification, comprising HCC as well as adjacent benign liver tissue (n=7) are provided. Further, for one patient shotgun protein identification was also performed in serum (blood) samples obtained after HCC recurrence.
